- Exact same design, colors ([SELECTED COLORS]), stitches ([SELECTED STITCHES])
- Exact same character and details - this is the same physical piece
- Only difference: displayed in a cozy home setting instead of product shot
- Warm lighting tone consistent with reference
- Accompanied by a few soft props: small potted plant, thread spools, or scissors
- Clean, warm, handmade aesthetic
- The embroidery is the focal point
- Natural, inviting home decor atmosphere
- Same neutral fabric and light wood hoop
- Proper fabric margin visible (0.5-1 inch between design and hoop edge) for authentic appearance

IF TEXT IS VISIBLE:
- Text must appear authentically hand-stitched (backstitch/stem stitch with visible individual stitches)
- Natural imperfections and organic character spacing
- NO font-like or computer-generated appearance
- Thread texture and dimension clearly visible

DO NOT ADD TEXT, TITLES, OR WORDS to the embroidery unless they appear in the reference design. Only show what is in the original piece.
[ADDITIONAL USER INSTRUCTIONS IF PROVIDED]
```

