### Variation 6: Marketing Photo (Vertical Social Media)

**Purpose:** Create vertical marketing image for Pinterest/Instagram with text overlays.

**Prompt:**
```
CRITICAL: The embroidery shown in this marketing image must be THE EXACT SAME piece from the reference image.

A vertical Pinterest/Instagram marketing image (1080×1350 aspect ratio) promoting the [SUBJECT] embroidery pattern. This is a promotional graphic designed for social media feeds.

EMBROIDERY (MANDATORY IDENTICAL):
- The finished embroidery must be EXACTLY the same as the reference image
- Same design, same colors ([SELECTED COLORS]), same stitches ([SELECTED STITCHES])
- Same character and all details - this is the same physical piece
- Same light wood hoop and neutral fabric
- Proper fabric margin visible (0.5-1 inch between design and hoop edge)

DO NOT ADD TEXT, TITLES, OR WORDS TO THE EMBROIDERY ITSELF unless they appear in the reference line drawing. The embroidery must strictly follow the approved design.

LAYOUT:
- Vertical orientation (portrait, taller than wide)
- Finished embroidery (from reference) in hoop as focal point
- Surrounded by scissors, thread skeins, pattern sheet, or styled props
- Leave open space at top or bottom for text overlay (OUTSIDE the embroidery area)
- Bright, natural lighting

TEXT OVERLAY REQUIREMENTS (for marketing graphics AROUND the photo, NOT on the embroidery):
Add clean, minimal text overlays OUTSIDE the embroidery area, using the brand color palette ([BRAND COLORS]):

[Top Section - in brand primary color]
"Embroidery Pattern PDF" or "Digital Embroidery Design"

[Middle Section - design title]
"[SUBJECT] Pattern" or "[SUBJECT] Embroidery Design"

[Bottom Section - details]
"Includes printable pattern + stitch guide"
"Perfect for beginners"
"Download instantly!"

TYPOGRAPHY & COLOR:
- Use maximum 2 fonts (one for headings, one for body)
- Text must be readable at mobile size
- Brand primary color for headings
- Neutral or brand secondary color for supporting text
- Excellent contrast between text and background
- Text placed in clear negative space zones AROUND the embroidery
- Do not obscure embroidery details
- Text overlay is ONLY for the marketing graphic frame, NOT stitched on the embroidery

- Embroidery from reference must be identical
- Bright, uplifting mood with natural lighting
- High resolution, Pinterest and Instagram ready
- Text overlay cleanly integrated in negative space
- Brand color palette used throughout
[ADDITIONAL USER INSTRUCTIONS IF PROVIDED]
```

**Inputs:**
- Line drawing image URL
- Hero embroidery image URL (as reference)
- Brand color palette

