## OUTPUT REFINEMENT CHECKLIST
⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻

Before finalizing your output, verify EVERY item on this checklist:
✅ Does the title START with what the item is (product type)?
✅ Does the title include "PDF" or "Digital Download" upfront?
✅ Are 2-3 key search phrases in the first 150 words of the description?
✅ Does the description start with a human hook?
✅ Does paragraph 1 mention "Digital download" or "PDF embroidery pattern"?
✅ Is there a benefit line explaining what the buyer gains?
✅ Does it include "perfect for beginner to intermediate stitchers" or similar?
✅ Does humor ENHANCE clarity rather than obscure it?
✅ Do the tags reflect audience intent, season, AND format?
✅ Are tags a 50/50 mix of broad and niche?
✅ Is there at least ONE seasonal AND ONE evergreen keyword?
✅ Is there at least ONE intent-based tag and ONE material-based tag?

If ANY item is not checked, adjust wording — don't add new sections. Keep structure intact.

⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻

Format your response as JSON with this structure:
{
  "title": "string (follow Etsy guidance: clear, concise, under 15 words, no repetition)",
  "description": "string (multi-paragraph)",
  "tags": "string (comma-separated for easy copy-paste: tag1, tag2, tag3, ...)",
  "listingDetails": {
    "category": "string",
    "attributes": ["attr1", "attr2", ...],
    "targetCustomer": "string",
    "occasions": ["occasion1", "occasion2", ...],
    "suggestedPriceRange": "string"
  },
  "instagramPost": {
    "caption": "string",
    "hashtags": ["tag1", "tag2", ...]
  },
  "pinterestPost": {
    "title": "string",
    "description": "string"
  },
  "seoTips": {
    "bestPostingTimes": ["time1", "time2", ...],
    "seasonalOpportunities": ["opp1", "opp2", ...],
    "relatedSearchTerms": ["term1", "term2", ...],
    "suggestedVariations": ["var1", "var2", ...]
  }
}
```

**Brand Voice Integration:**
- Fetches brand voice content from URL if provided
- Integrates throughout system and user prompts
- Emphasizes exact matching of voice, personality, humor, energy
- Warns against generic craft language when brand voice is specified

